    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, and you won\u2019t find a single flaw inside or out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
