      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential, both operating with factory-new precision. Significant preventative maintenance has been completed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The exterior retains its original luster with perfect panel gaps, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. A mechanically flawless example of BMW\u2019s ultimate driver\u2019s car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
